{"tid":2441230,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣將香港增列為中低風險地區　指香港疫情穩定控制中","createTime":"2021-03-10T13:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T15:02:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa350defb3ecaf1d03b8df9bf48145cff95c90b","tid":2441230,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:51:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579793-20210310.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579793-20210310.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPgQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=d2631c8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579793-20210310.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3b4bfccb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579793-20210310.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n在台灣，中央流行疫情指揮中心表示，香港疫情正在穩定控制中，已連續4個星期，達到中低風險分級標準，即日起將香港增列為中低風險地區。<br />\n<br />\n根據指揮中心的最新名單，與香港同列為中低感染風險的地方，亦包括新加坡、越南、柬埔寨及東帝汶等；被列為低感染風險的地方，就包括新西蘭、澳洲及澳門等。<br />\n<br />\n指揮中心呼籲民眾入境台灣時，如有發燒、咳嗽等不適症狀，應主動通報檢疫人員；入境後應落實居家檢疫，期間如出現疑似症狀，要主動聯絡衛生局或各縣市關懷中心，並依指示就醫，切勿乘搭公共交通工具。"},{"pid":"c978731ffc63a63e98cf94869d4c3463a0f4445c","tid":2441230,"uid":358940,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"佳仔可以去台灣了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad75ca1bcfc84d5e28eea76756e34945fc79d55","tid":2441230,"uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:56:56.000Z","msg":"去你老母，悶到死，係去都係日本啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3f2662382cac9084972621d56d2ccff2ec4da0","tid":2441230,"uid":338262,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1ad75ca1bcfc84d5e28eea76756e34945fc79d55","tid":2441230,"uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:56:56.000Z","msg":"去你老母，悶到